        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2009-01-21T17:33:21Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Robo COP Act: Robo Calls Off Phones - Directs the Federal Trade Commission (FTC), notwithstanding any other provision of law, to revise the do-not-call registry provisions of the Telemarketing Sales Rule to prohibit politically-oriented recorded message telephone calls to telephone numbers listed on that registry. </p> <p>Defines politically-oriented recorded message telephone call.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
    <title>Robo Calls Off Phones (Robo COP) Act</title>
